    <text>
        <body>
            <div xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to a friend (Linz, 17 February 1530)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1"> He knows how humane he usually is with his friends, and
                            therefore he will also do everything to accommodate his request.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb facs="https://www.eleveltar.hu/kereso-portlet/spring/digitalcontent/getcontent/preservica/39885315-93D6-4655-B639-072F63BDD16F
                    "/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Ad amicum.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Quis fueris et qualem te semper praestiteris, satis mihi constat, et
                    qua etiam humanitate in rebus tuorum amicorum usus fueris, iampridem multis
                    argumentis notum omnibus fecisti. Ego vicissim quid in rebus tuis facere
                    potuerim mihi demandatis, tute melius scis, quam <del corresp="Olahus"
                        >aliis</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr">alii</add>. Non passus sum pro
                    mea facultate meum abs te officium desiderari. Quare quid me deinceps facere
                        <del corresp="Olahus">opteat</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr"
                        >oporteat</add>, fac me certiorem, deinceps quoque eandem, quam hactenus
                    praestabo <del corresp="Olahus">operam</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="insert"
                        >operam</add> et diligentiam. Tu pariter non sis tui dissimilis, sed in ea,
                    quam in hunc diem amplexus es, humanitate permane. Vale et me ama.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Ex <placeName>Lincio</placeName> 17. Februarii 1530.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
